headline.main: Manned Balloon Sent Into Low Stratosphere

results.snippet: WASHINGTON, May 6 (AP) -- Two scientists were headed into the lower stratosphere tonight in a balloon launched from an open iron mine near Crosby, Minn., the Navy announced.
